---
title: Chermoula Beef Kofta & Curry Sauce with Cucumber Salad & Rapid Rice
description: It’s beef koftas and fluffy rice tonight, and we know it’s going to be a new favourite when you get a taste of that Bengal curry glaze! All you need is some crunch from the cucumber salad and there you have it - another home-run for weeknight dinners.
